[1] Americas
[A] USA
Date: Tue 20 Dec 2022 05:58 AM IST
Source: LatestLY [edited]
https://www.latestly.com/socially/world/weekly-u-s-influenza-update-seasonal-flu-declining-in-some-areas-cases-15-million-latest-tweet-by-bno-feed-4604924.html


Weekly US influenza update: seasonal flu declining in some areas
----------------------------------------------------------------
- Cases: 15 million (+2 million)
- Hospitalizations: 150 000 (+30 000)
- Deaths: 9300 (+2000)
- Most common strain: A(H3N2)
- Pediatric deaths: 30 (+9)

